  "title": "Hair Care Consultant | Gross up to $2700| 5.5 Working Days | Island wide - ZH",
  "description": "<p>Location: Island wide<br />Salary: Gross up to $3000<br />Working Hours: 9 Hours Shift (Retail Hours)</p><p>Key Duties:</p><ul><li>Provide professional consultation and advise customers on the possible treatments and</li><li>solutions.</li><li>Provide hands-on hair & scalp treatment and follow up with customers.</li><li>Perform General duties including answering phone calls, handle point of sales system when needed.</li></ul><p>Key Requirements:</p><ul><li>Prior sales experience (preferably in beauty wellness, or hair care industry) with Spa/Salon setting experience.</li></ul><p>WhatsApp me at wa.me/6587801169 or press the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your resume and/or personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal data by the company (or its designated agent) for the purposes of processing, administration and managing your job application.</p><p>Please be notified that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Sim Shu Hui Reg No.: R25129789<br />Griffin HR Consultancy Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 23C1449</p>",
